itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 3/24/2022.

Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing everything under the sun from Sharki B on Nickelodeon to social media destroying the world.
